name: Eternal end
description:
This is a space exploration game. People have always longed for space. Finally, you have the opportunity to explore space, piloting cool fighter jets to explore the vast starry sky. But in the mysterious space, besides you, there are many other positions and situations. There is danger ahead, and there are constantly falling rocks. Are you a warrior? Do you dare to challenge yourself?

Gameplay

You need to control the fighter jet and constantly avoid the upcoming boulders

When you are hit by a boulder, you will fail!

Game operation mode

Mobile=WASD

Attack=Left Mouse Button

Game features

Air combat games mainly emphasize realistic operational feel.

A tense and exciting game that constantly tests your observation ability.
